other objects.description: There is a red object on the ground on the right side of the road near the parked white car, but it is unidentifiable - possible debris or fallen object.
other objects.explanation: The ego vehicle should maintain a safe distance and be prepared to avoid it if necessary.

suggestions: Proceed with caution, especially due to the potential debris on the right side of the road and the lack of visibility of traffic lights or signs. The ego car should remain alert to the parked vehicle on the right and the oncoming vehicle to ensure a safe passage through the intersection. Reduce speed if necessary to allow for adequate response time to unexpected events.
